teen-and-the-e-street-band-announce-support-acts-for-london-bst-hyde-park-shows-3433181">在伦敦 BST 海德公园举行的两晚头条节目</a>。</p><p>这位 74 岁的摇滚老将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-cancels-two-us-shows-after-being-taken-ill-3484313">在 8 月份患上了当时未公开的疾病</a>，导致费城的两场演出被取消。三周后，当斯普林斯汀被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-shares-health-update-on-monster-peptic-ulcer-3512936">诊断出患有消化性溃疡</a>时，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-being-treated-for-peptic-ulcer-disease-symptoms-postpones-all-september-shows-3494366">九月的所有巡演日期都被推迟</a>。</p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-announces-rescheduled-us-tour-dates-for-2024-buy-tickets-3510869">他重新安排了受影响的美国演出</a>，并向歌迷确认他将在 2024 年 3 月至 9 月之间开始巡演。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fbruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-tickets%2Fartist%2F860453" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到剩余的美国演出门票。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-adds-second-london-show-to-2024-uk-and-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3530088">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 为 2024 年英国和爱尔兰巡演添加第二场伦敦演出后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
